show.title: Eternal Love
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/BgPZsu
show.description: Wealthy businessman Vikram escapes his daughter’s matchmaking by lying he’s married. Avni, also pretending for family pressure, crosses paths with him while seeking a fake marriage certificate. They agree to a no-strings union, unaware fate has other plans. After an accident, Avni reenters Vikram’s life as his office cleaner. Forced to pose as his wife, love grows amid secrets and chaos. When they move to divorce, they discover they had been truly married all along.
